text: Horney is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Brigitte Horney (1911–1988), German actress * Karen Horney (1885–1952), German psychoanalyst * Jane Horney (1918–1945), Swedish woman, believed to have spied in Denmark for the benefit of Nazi Germany ==See also== * Norwood, Ohio v.
